meta_title: Caulk Backer Rod
short_description: DAP Caulk Backer Rod is closed-cell polyethylene foam that is used to fill large joints before caulking. It works with most caulks and sealants by saving expensive caulk and preventing joint failure by partially filling large joints before applying caulk or sealant. Backer rod can also improve the energy efficiency of a home by helping to insulate and prevent drafts. Use it indoors or outdoors on a variety of projects including windows and doors, wall joints, foundations and cracks in pavement.
meta_keyword: Caulk Backer Rod

meta_title: Eclipse™ Rapid Wall Repair Patch
short_description: Eclipse™ Rapid Wall Repair Patches are a unique and innovative drywall repair solution that is perfect for completing permanent repairs on damaged walls and ceilings. No more waiting for spackling to dry or messy sanding. DAP Eclipse allows you to patch drywall damage and paint immediately, allowing you to finish your project faster. This all-in-one, mess free solution not only provides a permanent, long-lasting repair but also superior impact resistance for areas that may see reoccurring impact, such as behind a door.  4X stronger than drywall itself - Superior impact resistance All-in-one, mess free - No spackling, sanding or tools required Finish project faster - Paint immediately & finish in minutes Permanent, long-lasting - Won't peel or lose adhesion over time
